    {"id": "rev_szb_01", "target_type": "attraction", "target_id": "attr_shenzhen_bay", "content": "深圳湾公园太美了！傍晚来散步看日落，还能远眺香港。13公里滨海栈道很适合骑行。", "sentiment": "positive", "source_files": ["sf_01"]},
    {"id": "rev_lh_01", "target_type": "attraction", "target_id": "attr_lianhua_mountain", "content": "莲花山公园是俯瞰深圳CBD的最佳地点，邓小平铜像广场视野开阔，夜景也很美。", "sentiment": "positive", "source_files": ["sf_01"]},
    {"id": "rev_dm_01", "target_type": "attraction", "target_id": "attr_dongmen", "content": "东门老街人太多了，商业化严重，但小吃确实多。注意保管好随身物品。", "sentiment": "mixed", "source_files": ["sf_01"]},
